r writing test Benefits: Work from home opportunities Flexible working hours Contract length: 12 months Part-time hours: 10-40 per week Job Types: Full-time, Part-time, Contract Salary: $50.00 to $250.00 /hour Schedule: Monday to Friday Experience: Copywriting: 2 years (Preferred) Application Question: This is a fun copywriting role that will provide daily work. We do require short 24-hour turn around on your copy. What concerns you with this? "
